# Code Owners for Code-Guardian
# 
# This file defines who should be automatically requested for review
# when certain files are modified in pull requests.
#
# More info: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Global owners - these users will be requested for review on all PRs
* @d-oit

# Root configuration files
/.github/ @d-oit
/Cargo.toml @d-oit
/Cargo.lock @d-oit
/rustfmt.toml @d-oit
/.gitignore @d-oit
/README.md @d-oit
/CONTRIBUTING.md @d-oit
/CHANGELOG.md @d-oit
/LICENSE @d-oit

# CI/CD and automation
